	</div>

	<div class="docs-reference">
		<h2 class="example_subtitle code-copy">column--span-(n)</h2>
		<p>Required span class (min 1, max = selected column total)<br>Similar to the table cell attribute <span class="code-copy">col-span</span>, sets the number of spaces a column spans.</p>
